statements.sql: select * from "users" where "id" = 1 and "users"."deleted_at" is null limit 1

select "permissions".*, "permission_role"."role_id" as "pivot_role_id", "permission_role"."permission_id" as "pivot_permission_id" from "permissions" inner join "permission_role" on "permissions"."id" = "permission_role"."permission_id" where "permission_role"."role_id" in (1, 2) and "permissions"."deleted_at" is null

select * from "im_conversations" where exists (select * from "users" inner join "im_recipients" on "users"."id" = "im_recipients"."user_id" where "im_conversations"."id" = "im_recipients"."conversation_id" and "id" = 1) and "im_conversations"."deleted_at" is null order by "updated_at" desc limit 1000 offset 0

select "roles".*, "role_user"."user_id" as "pivot_user_id", "role_user"."role_id" as "pivot_role_id" from "roles" inner join "role_user" on "roles"."id" = "role_user"."role_id" where "role_user"."user_id" = 1 and "roles"."deleted_at" is null
select exists(select * from "roles" inner join "role_user" on "roles"."id" = "role_user"."role_id" where "role_user"."user_id" = 1 and "title" = 'Admin' and "roles"."deleted_at" is null) as "exists"
select count(*) as aggregate from "clients" where "clients"."deleted_at" is null
select * from "teams" where "teams"."id" = 1 and "teams"."deleted_at" is null limit 1
